abstract: >-
  A novel framework that maps agentic AI capabilities to innovation process phases.
  Introduces the Orchestrated Feedback Hierarchy (OFH), Dissent-as-Innovation-Signal,
  Startup Genome & IT-Score, Ethical Friction, and a Two-Layer Knowledge Architecture.
